{"tid":2421624,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"千奇唔好租觀塘有利中心3樓 de CONCEPT","createTime":"2021-02-24T15:31:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T09:02:05.000Z","uid":254192,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc32c65e7ef194b5f2fb28e3504746f7b84afe1","tid":2421624,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:31:15.000Z","msg":"幾乎9成單位收唔到訊號<br />\n聲稱1000Mbps wifi 每個月都壞1個禮拜<br />\n冇得上網點做嘢呀你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連你想自己駁私人寬頻都唔可以<br />\n管理公司處理速度反應極慢 <br />\n叫佢搵個師傅黎處理次次都話要搵大業主商量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你老母次次回覆都係答非所問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n租左呢度之後每個月要被逼無預警WFH at least 1個禮拜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次重要撞正最忙既時候 我真係屌你老母臭西<br />\n<br />\n除此之外呢度租左幾個月以來廁所啲尿兜壞曬完全冇人理過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廁所臭到飛天都冇人處理<br />\n冷氣機滴水滴到水浸浸到人地studio入面都見過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩我唔係租係冷氣機隔離 如果唔係浸爛曬入面啲貨同家私都唔知邊個賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要係今次我真係忍無可忍 wifi 寬頻壞左成4/5日<br />\n個管理公司仲要斯斯然話大概要再2-3日先會有翻網絡<br />\n我真係屌你老母臭西 你係咪會賠番啲租金比我呀<br />\n你估我租黎托柒架你老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">千奇唔好租 觀塘開源道45號有利中心3樓 de CONCEPT</span></strong></span> <br />\n伏到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8772a5abeca367a3a7315add8ef439f9def992","tid":2421624,"uid":38904,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"喺度開post有閪用咩<br />\n99%連登仔連自己層樓月租都未畀得起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20462b55937e451694bbe